The engineering society sponsors a resume review table near the stage, and camera crews capture interviews throughout the event.

At the entrance, staff scan registrations and distribute lanyards, while interview sign-up sheets fill with names as attendees use tablets at kiosks to upload resumes. Small groups analyze enthusiastic recruiters and rehearse elevator pitches, while friends decompress on the quad, discussing responses from companies and marking target employers on event maps. The aroma of coffee and catered snacks wafts from the lounge, where alumni volunteers offer pep talks. A data science company showcases a live dashboard of attendance, and an alumni panel provides insights on preparing for technical interviews. As the day winds down, volunteers stack collapsed booths and gather leftover brochures.

Concurrently, career center staff log attendance metrics on laptops, and announcement chimes signal the final hour of the event. A welcome announcement outlines the fair schedule over the PA system. Friends decompress on the quad, sharing their experiences about company responses. Volunteers stack collapsed booths and gather leftover brochures on the polished floor, where dozens of colorful banners from various booths are displayed. In an adjoining classroom, workshops on networking etiquette begin, and a small drone from a robotics startup flies above its booth to attract attention. A whiteboard lists employers scheduling same-day interviews, and a post-event survey link flashes on monitors near the exit. Camera crews capture interviews, and a data science company showcases a live dashboard of fair attendance.

Staff scan registrations and distribute lanyards at the entrance, while interview sign-up sheets fill with names as the day winds down and students use tablets at kiosks to upload resumes to the fair database. Attendees receive tote bags filled with items such as business cards, branded notebooks, pens, water bottles, and phone chargers. Groups of friends mark target employers on the event map and analyze enthusiastic recruiters while decompressing in the lounge, where the aroma of coffee and catered snacks spreads. A data science company showcases a live dashboard of attendance, and additional tech firms feature demo screens displaying their latest apps.

Inside, staff scan registrations, distribute lanyards, and monitor a live dashboard of fair attendance; attendees receive tote bags filled with branded notebooks, pens, water bottles, and phone chargers, with some quietly rehearsing elevator pitches. The lounge fills with the aroma of coffee and catered snacks, where alumni volunteers offer pep talks, and an alumni panel discusses preparing for technical interviews. Monitors display a post-event survey link, and during the final hour, interview sign-up sheets attract attention. As the event winds down, students gather in the quad to discuss target employers while volunteers manage booth breakdown and leftover materials.
